title: How to Breakthrough
itunes:title: How to Breakthrough
description:
Episode 513 - In order for our lives to change we need a breakthrough. Something that makes us say "enough is enough!" or "I am no longer happy with the way my life is!" Something that enables us to make the decision to completely remodel our lives and make them better. In this episode, I talk about how to create that breakthrough.
